data.title: List of NES Games (North America)
data.meta_description: Below is a list of every video game released for the Nintendo Entertainment System (NES) in the United States of America (USA) and Canada. This list comprises a total of 837 titles. 677 Licensed Titles & 160 Unlicensed Titles 677 Licensed Titles released in the USA 160 Unlicensed Titles relea...
